                     <Label style="-fx-font-size: 20px; -fx-font-weight: bold;" text="Get to Work on Time" />
                     <Label text="Finding a parking space is poison. But not anymore! Book a parking space in advance and from anywhere, so you don't waste time on the road. Thanks to the online reservation system, you won't have to travel to work an hour early to find a place to park. This will save you not only time but also stress from finding vacancies in the city." wrapText="true" />

                     <Label style="-fx-font-size: 20px; -fx-font-weight: bold;" text="No Mess in the Parking Lot" />
                     <Label text="The online reservation system helps to make better use of the parking spaces in the building. Thanks to a simple overview, employees can book a place only on the days when they really need it. Bookigy supports bookings across multiple buildings, so you can secure a seat at any of your branches. And you can also reserve a parking space for visitors such as business partners." wrapText="true" />
                  </children>
               </VBox>
            </children>
         </VBox>

